{"tid":2369474,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"事業看最高分、學業看平均分、生活看最低分","createTime":"2021-01-17T07:22:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-18T11:53:42.000Z","uid":389615,"like":6,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2613d615ee0ea67ee00b8d97480544e0222992e3","tid":2369474,"uid":389615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T07:22:47.000Z","msg":"工作事業看最高分、學業成績看平均分、生活質素看最低分<br />\n<br />\n工作與事業：因為現代社會講專門化和分工，所以你應該Specialize係你最強，比較優勢最好的地方發展。所以工作與事業成就，看最高分的成績決定。<br />\n<br />\n學業成績：一般學校都係計平均分，語文科要合格。學業成績，看平均分的成績決定。<br />\n<br />\n生活質素：假設你的健康，差不多樣樣都很好，樣樣都A級，但你肝臟不好，肝功能差，肝臟F級。那麼你的健康是甚麼水平 ? 對不起，不是B級，而是F級。如果你很富有，財富A級，健康F級，你的生活當然就是F級。同樣，如果你很窮，但健康，你財富F級，健康A級，你生活同樣是F級。因為生活質素，不是計平均分，而係以你最低分那項做決定。"},{"pid":"87a126f62d3df1f19c54c8661157ce979bb7799c","tid":2369474,"uid":389615,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2613d615ee0ea67ee00b8d97480544e0222992e3","tid":2369474,"uid":389615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T07:22:47.000Z","msg":"工作事業看最高分、學業成績看平均分、生活質素看最低分<br />\n<br />\n工作與事業：因為現代社會講專門化和分工，所以你應該Specialize係你最強，比較優勢最好的地方發展。所以工作與事業成就，看最高分的成績決定。<br />\n<br />\n學業成績：一般學校都係計平均分，語文科要合格。學業成績，看平均分的成績決定。<br />\n<br />\n生活質素：假設你的健康，差不多樣樣都很好，樣樣都A級，但你肝臟不好，肝功能差，肝臟F級。那麼你的健康是甚麼水平 ? 對不起，不是B級，而是F級。如果你很富有，財富A級，健康F級，你的生活當然就是F級。同樣，如果你很窮，但健康，你財富F級，健康A級，你生活同樣是F級。因為生活質素，不是計平均分，而係以你最低分那項做決定。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T07:25:14.000Z","msg":"呢樣雖然係常識，不過很多人都忽略左。<br />\n<br />\n有些人成日問： 有錢好把閉啊，有錢人又點點點，健康最重要云云。無錯，有錢唔一定把閉，但健康無錢都無用。因為錢只係生活其中一項，健康也是其中一項。生活質素，係看最低分那項做決定，而不是平均分或最高分決定你的生活質素。"},{"pid":"0fe6b1a39f790d0a9883d3d3e7320583d08a6b7e","tid":2369474,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T07:26:28.000Z","msg":"學業睇平均分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即係樓豬冇考AL/DSE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><p class=\"right\"></p>"},{"pid":"1d429646a538c76566994614fdba398cd092ab14","tid":2369474,"uid":389615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0fe6b1a39f790d0a9883d3d3e7320583d08a6b7e","tid":2369474,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T07:26:28.000Z","msg":"學業睇平均分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即係樓豬冇考AL/DSE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><p class=\"right\"></p>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T07:27:19.000Z","msg":"係CE/AL/DSE先看最佳幾科。<br />\n上到大學，GPA咪又係講平均分。"},{"pid":"e8cb43ed54674fe30a054e66e03565e879ee892f","tid":2369474,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1d429646a538c76566994614fdba398cd092ab14","tid":2369474,"uid":389615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0fe6b1a39f790d0a9883d3d3e7320583d08a6b7e","tid":2369474,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T07:26:28.000Z","msg":"學業睇平均分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即係樓豬冇考AL/DSE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><p class=\"right\"></p>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T07:27:19.000Z","msg":"係CE/AL/DSE先看最佳幾科。<br />\n上到大學，GPA咪又係講平均分。"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T07:29:08.000Z","msg":"大學同工作一樣specialize咗<br />\n如果你認為工作係specialize，而大學係睇平均，咁你啲logic太跳脫<br />\n<br />\nHon GPA同CGPA唔係同一樣嘢"},{"pid":"f08075b0c2b5c60c5b1b7718878e985fda7e546a","tid":2369474,"uid":389615,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"e8cb43ed54674fe30a054e66e03565e879ee892f","tid":2369474,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1d429646a538c76566994614fdba398cd092ab14","tid":2369474,"uid":389615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0fe6b1a39f790d0a9883d3d3e7320583d08a6b7e","tid":2369474,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T07:26:28.000Z","msg":"學業睇平均分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即係樓豬冇考AL/DSE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><p class=\"right\"></p>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T07:27:19.000Z","msg":"係CE/AL/DSE先看最佳幾科。<br />\n上到大學，GPA咪又係講平均分。"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T07:29:08.000Z","msg":"大學同工作一樣specialize咗<br />\n如果你認為工作係specialize，而大學係睇平均，咁你啲logic太跳脫<br />\n<br />\nHon GPA同CGPA唔係同一樣嘢"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T07:36:56.000Z","msg":"其實學業計分，具體係看學制的。<br />\n<strong>大多數學制都係計平均分，所以我講係平均分。</strong><br />\n<strong>即使係DSE，都係計平均分，不過係最佳5科的平均分。</strong><br />\n即使係AL，都係計平均分，不過係最佳4科的平均分。<br />\n<br />\n如果你生活，係計最低分，其實細節上，<br />\n都係計關鍵的器官健康(如腦、心臟、肝臟、肺部、腎臟、腸胃、喉嚨、鼻子) 、心理及精神健康、財富之中最低分那樣。"},{"pid":"60dd62d18d1ecfa77fde00bd14b0056846dcd641","tid":2369474,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f08075b0c2b5c60c5b1b7718878e985fda7e546a","tid":2369474,"uid":389615,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"e8cb43ed54674fe30a054e66e03565e879ee892f","tid":2369474,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1d429646a538c76566994614fdba398cd092ab14","tid":2369474,"uid":389615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T07:27:19.000Z","msg":"係CE/AL/DSE先看最佳幾科。<br />\n上到大學，GPA咪又係講平均分。"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T07:29:08.000Z","msg":"大學同工作一樣specialize咗<br />\n如果你認為工作係specialize，而大學係睇平均，咁你啲logic太跳脫<br />\n<br />\nHon GPA同CGPA唔係同一樣嘢"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T07:36:56.000Z","msg":"其實學業計分，具體係看學制的。<br />\n<strong>大多數學制都係計平均分，所以我講係平均分。</strong><br />\n<strong>即使係DSE，都係計平均分，不過係最佳5科的平均分。</strong><br />\n即使係AL，都係計平均分，不過係最佳4科的平均分。<br />\n<br />\n如果你生活，係計最低分，其實細節上，<br />\n都係計關鍵的器官健康(如腦、心臟、肝臟、肺部、腎臟、腸胃、喉嚨、鼻子) 、心理及精神健康、財富之中最低分那樣。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T07:37:50.000Z","msg":"高中要揀科<br />\n入u有weighting"},{"pid":"2ba85e714d90f7e513b49c7551edf63cabd8f3f3","tid":2369474,"uid":389615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60dd62d18d1ecfa77fde00bd14b0056846dcd641","tid":2369474,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f08075b0c2b5c60c5b1b7718878e985fda7e546a","tid":2369474,"uid":389615,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"e8cb43ed54674fe30a054e66e03565e879ee892f","tid":2369474,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T07:29:08.000Z","msg":"大學同工作一樣specialize咗<br />\n如果你認為工作係specialize，而大學係睇平均，咁你啲logic太跳脫<br />\n<br />\nHon GPA同CGPA唔係同一樣嘢"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T07:36:56.000Z","msg":"其實學業計分，具體係看學制的。<br />\n<strong>大多數學制都係計平均分，所以我講係平均分。</strong><br />\n<strong>即使係DSE，都係計平均分，不過係最佳5科的平均分。</strong><br />\n即使係AL，都係計平均分，不過係最佳4科的平均分。<br />\n<br />\n如果你生活，係計最低分，其實細節上，<br />\n都係計關鍵的器官健康(如腦、心臟、肝臟、肺部、腎臟、腸胃、喉嚨、鼻子) 、心理及精神健康、財富之中最低分那樣。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T07:37:50.000Z","msg":"高中要揀科<br />\n入u有weighting"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T07:39:32.000Z","msg":"<strong>具體睇學制，不過多數(主流方向)都係計平均分。</strong><br />\n<br />\nU計Credit，AGPA先計Weight。"},{"pid":"4279ddb9cfce4108e25a27ffbde532446b182ed0","tid":2369474,"uid":389615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8cb43ed54674fe30a054e66e03565e879ee892f","tid":2369474,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1d429646a538c76566994614fdba398cd092ab14","tid":2369474,"uid":389615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0fe6b1a39f790d0a9883d3d3e7320583d08a6b7e","tid":2369474,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T07:26:28.000Z","msg":"學業睇平均分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即係樓豬冇考AL/DSE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><p class=\"right\"></p>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T07:27:19.000Z","msg":"係CE/AL/DSE先看最佳幾科。<br />\n上到大學，GPA咪又係講平均分。"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T07:29:08.000Z","msg":"大學同工作一樣specialize咗<br />\n如果你認為工作係specialize，而大學係睇平均，咁你啲logic太跳脫<br />\n<br />\nHon GPA同CGPA唔係同一樣嘢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T07:43:10.000Z","msg":"具體都係睇學制。<br />\n通常越接近職業培訓 (大學，或者考大學) 就走 Specialize方向，即係最佳幾科。<br />\n<strong>接近基礎教育(小學, 初中)就計平均分。</strong>"},{"pid":"73962b157e17bbaf38e38fe8100cf7f6a3ac234c","tid":2369474,"uid":389615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T07:43:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>學業睇平均分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即係樓豬冇考AL/DSE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><p class=\"right\"></p></blockquote>係CE/AL/DSE先看最佳幾科。<br />\n上到大學，GPA咪又係講平均分。</blockquote>大學同工作一樣specialize咗<br />\n如果你認為工作係specialize，而大學係睇平均，咁你啲logic太跳脫<br />\n<br />\nHon GPA同CGPA唔係同一樣嘢</blockquote>具體都係睇學制。<br />\n通常越<strong>接近職業培訓 (大學，或者考大學) 就走 Specialize方向</strong>，<strong>即係最佳幾科</strong>。<br />\n<strong>接近基礎教育(小學, 初中)就計平均分。</strong></blockquote>"},{"pid":"7d821a117394566f254df82e3e1f8bd290506994","tid":2369474,"uid":389615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T07:51:00.000Z","msg":"更正: <br />\n工作事業看最高分、學業成績<strong>主要</strong>看平均分、生活質素看最低分<br />\n<br />\n工作與事業：<strong>因為現代社會講專門化和分工，所以你應該Specialize係你最強</strong>，比較優勢最好的地方發展。所以工作與事業成就，看最高分的成績決定。<br />\n<br />\n學業成績：一<strong>般學校都係計平均分</strong>，語文科要合格。學業成績，看平均分的成績決定。<strong>不過，因為讀書某程度上都為職業與事業發展，所以某些學制會用最佳幾科的平均分或總分計算。</strong><br />\n<br />\n生活質素：假設你的健康，差不多樣樣都很好，樣樣都A級，但你肝臟不好，肝功能差，肝臟F級。那麼你的健康是甚麼水平 ? 對不起，不是B級，而是F級。<strong>如果你很富有，財富A級，健康F級，你的生活當然就是F級。</strong>同樣，如果<strong>你很窮，但健康，你財富F級，健康A級，你生活同樣是F級</strong>。因為生活質素，不是計平均分，而係以你最低分那項做決定。"},{"pid":"2a85fff1a3728e13f5b70924ea9a57ee52957282","tid":2369474,"uid":77968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T13:54:45.000Z","msg":"樓主忽略左佔比<br />\n人生咁長，生活80年，事業40年，學業20年<br />\n證明左咩？人類大多數時間都被最低標準影響緊自己，被高要求佔左一半人生"},{"pid":"b323d0edc71d402edb9e6064de0dbbd51881ef47","tid":2369474,"uid":389615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a85fff1a3728e13f5b70924ea9a57ee52957282","tid":2369474,"uid":77968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T13:54:45.000Z","msg":"樓主忽略左佔比<br />\n人生咁長，生活80年，事業40年，學業20年<br />\n證明左咩？人類大多數時間都被最低標準影響緊自己，被高要求佔左一半人生"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T13:58:38.000Z","msg":"應該說是世界設計者設計的特性。<br />\n生活質素就是看你表現最脆弱那環。"},{"pid":"b7306e635b3a07dbfa0a7703792c99c49226a7d6","tid":2369474,"uid":342891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8cb43ed54674fe30a054e66e03565e879ee892f","tid":2369474,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1d429646a538c76566994614fdba398cd092ab14","tid":2369474,"uid":389615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0fe6b1a39f790d0a9883d3d3e7320583d08a6b7e","tid":2369474,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T07:26:28.000Z","msg":"學業睇平均分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即係樓豬冇考AL/DSE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><p class=\"right\"></p>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T07:27:19.000Z","msg":"係CE/AL/DSE先看最佳幾科。<br />\n上到大學，GPA咪又係講平均分。"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T07:29:08.000Z","msg":"大學同工作一樣specialize咗<br />\n如果你認為工作係specialize，而大學係睇平均，咁你啲logic太跳脫<br />\n<br />\nHon GPA同CGPA唔係同一樣嘢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T08:03:30.000Z","msg":"Specialisation 好多時都係學位之後而不在大學，就如香港醫生的專科訓練並不在大學"},{"pid":"7eede7756d350d9cce4882e316c6d34f5e0aab6b","tid":2369474,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7306e635b3a07dbfa0a7703792c99c49226a7d6","tid":2369474,"uid":342891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8cb43ed54674fe30a054e66e03565e879ee892f","tid":2369474,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1d429646a538c76566994614fdba398cd092ab14","tid":2369474,"uid":389615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T07:27:19.000Z","msg":"係CE/AL/DSE先看最佳幾科。<br />\n上到大學，GPA咪又係講平均分。"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T07:29:08.000Z","msg":"大學同工作一樣specialize咗<br />\n如果你認為工作係specialize，而大學係睇平均，咁你啲logic太跳脫<br />\n<br />\nHon GPA同CGPA唔係同一樣嘢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T08:03:30.000Z","msg":"Specialisation 好多時都係學位之後而不在大學，就如香港醫生的專科訓練並不在大學"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T08:22:13.000Z","msg":"初中讀全科<br />